Class WordOfRecall

  • java.lang.Object
    • javelin.controller.upgrade.Upgrade
      • javelin.model.unit.abilities.spell.Spell
        • javelin.model.unit.abilities.spell.conjuration.teleportation.WordOfRecall
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class WordOfRecall
extends Spell
    Brings you back to last visited town. See the d20 SRD for more info. Assumes caster level 20 to be able to transport as many creatures as willed. Destination for this spell is set when the spell is prepared, not when it's cast, so it makes some sense that that a Scroll could also be prepared before being cast. It's a bit of a stretch but doing anything else would be very complicated considering the numberr of different ways an Item can be generated in Javelin. http://paizo.com/pathfinderRPG/prd/coreRulebook/spells/wordOfRecall.html
